Functional Requirements Table - Langol Krishi Sahayak

FR-1: Registration System
Description: The system shall allow farmers, experts, customers, and data operators to register with role-specific information and document verification to create secure user accounts
Stakeholders: Admin, Farmer, Expert, Customer, Data Operator
Priority: High

FR-2: Authentication System  
Description: The system should authenticate users before granting access to its features and functionalities to ensure security and privacy with role-based login
Stakeholders: Admin, Farmer, Expert, Customer, Data Operator
Priority: High

FR-3: Profile Management
Description: The system shall allow users to view, edit, and manage their profile information with session management to maintain updated user data
Stakeholders: Admin, Farmer, Expert, Customer, Data Operator
Priority: Medium

FR-4: Crop Recommendation System
Description: The system shall provide AI-driven crop recommendations based on location, season, soil conditions, and profitability analysis to help farmers make informed decisions
Stakeholders: Farmer, Admin
Priority: High

FR-5: Crop Planning Guideline
Description: The system shall provide detailed crop planning guidelines including planting schedules, care instructions, and best practices to support successful farming
Stakeholders: Farmer, Expert
Priority: Medium

FR-6: Disease Diagnosis System
Description: The system shall provide AI-powered disease diagnosis through image analysis and symptom description with treatment recommendations to help farmers identify and treat crop diseases
Stakeholders: Farmer, Expert
Priority: High

FR-7: Expert Consultation
Description: The system shall facilitate farmer-expert consultation through multiple communication channels with request tracking to provide professional agricultural guidance
Stakeholders: Farmer, Expert
Priority: High

FR-8: Social Feed System
Description: The system shall provide a community platform for sharing posts, images, discussions, and agricultural knowledge to foster collaboration among users
Stakeholders: Admin, Farmer, Expert, Customer
Priority: Medium

FR-9: Weather Forecasting
Description: The system shall provide current weather conditions, 7-day forecasts, and agricultural planning recommendations to help users plan farming activities
Stakeholders: Admin, Farmer, Expert, Customer
Priority: High

FR-10: Marketplace System
Description: The system shall provide a marketplace for buying, selling, and renting agricultural products and equipment to facilitate agricultural commerce
Stakeholders: Farmer, Customer, Admin
Priority: High

FR-11: Market Price Information
Description: The system shall display real-time market prices, trends, and comparative pricing across different markets to help users make informed trading decisions
Stakeholders: Farmer, Customer
Priority: Medium

FR-12: Agricultural News and Policy
Description: The system shall provide categorized agricultural news, policy updates, and government announcements to keep users informed about agricultural developments
Stakeholders: Admin, Farmer, Expert, Customer
Priority: Medium

FR-13: Expert Dashboard
Description: The system shall provide experts with consultation management, request queuing, and response tracking capabilities to efficiently manage their services
Stakeholders: Expert, Admin
Priority: High

FR-14: Crop & Diagnosis Management
Description: The system shall allow experts to review farmer submissions, provide diagnosis, and manage crop-related consultations to deliver professional agricultural services
Stakeholders: Expert, Farmer
Priority: High

FR-15: Profile Verification
Description: The system shall enable data operators to verify and approve user profiles and submitted documents to ensure data accuracy and user authenticity
Stakeholders: Data Operator, Admin
Priority: High
